{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"7b50ae70accc7b99b8c74ffb204c7f610a93c98749f6d9badfe16de68a66a317","slug":"zstu-bigdata-micro-major","location":"/roadmap/qtclass/zstu_bigdata_micro_major.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"浙理大数据微专业工作蓝图","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":2}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/roadmap/qtclass/zstu_bigdata_micro_major.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/roadmap/qtclass/zstu_bigdata_micro_major.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"zstu_bigdata_micro_major.md","url":"/zstu_bigdata_micro_m-7cd2e4cf25790bc4211f29c4d71d2c03.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们的定位","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"sFvdzHunZB"}],"identifier":"id","label":"我们的定位","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"O3ElzEE3nE"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"浙江理工大学计算机系是我们产教融合模式的典型合作案例。他们甚至为了我们打破了企业掏钱给高校合作的传统，第一次主动掏钱给企业做校企合作课程。我们非常感谢学校的认可和敬佩老师们的改革精神，也愿意尽我们所能互惠互利。","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"jWG43GBz65"}],"key":"vhp8ph7QnN"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们先后负责了生产实习课程、主修的大数据理论课和实践课、大数据微专业整个项目的教学改革工作。同时还参与了主修大数据课程设置改革的咨询工作。","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"TOQPsyczVC"}],"key":"GRkSBXbRVq"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"核心竞争力","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"EUb7Y6v9hA"}],"identifier":"id","label":"核心竞争力","html_id":"id-1","implicit":true,"key":"jT6qf0RBZI"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们能在这个合作中站住脚，靠的不是传统教育机构的课程设计能力，而是把一线业务实践转化为教学内容的真实经验。","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"KkiU50NRJF"}],"key":"CukkT01DGn"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在我的建议下，数据工程、数据挖掘等工程性和实用性很强的课程得以进入课表，并且大量地引入了我们在业务上的实践，以及最新的使用大模型处理数据的经验。这是高校自己难以快速做到的事情——教材更新永远追不上技术变化，而我们的优势就是活在技术变化的第一线。","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"VJOWubGlTW"}],"key":"KOwVEDBVRC"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们的经营困难","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"RxChfLvz59"}],"identifier":"id","label":"我们的经营困难","html_id":"id-2","implicit":true,"key":"XjQ8x8mDZD"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"校企合作的典型矛盾是节奏错配。高校的教学计划周期长、审批链多，而我们的业务节奏快、迭代频繁。如何在固定的学期框架内嵌入快速变化的内容，是一个持续需要磨合的问题。","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"pK1OhXCOiY"}],"key":"qPLLJZX8sJ"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"另外，高校预算敏感，虽然浙理工打破了传统主动出资，但整体上这类合作的经济模型仍然很薄，需要靠高效率来维持。","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"WvZhHQpsuA"}],"key":"tU230dIfB7"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"课程体系架构","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"key":"wME4LWkCnx"}],"identifier":"id","label":"课程体系架构","html_id":"id-3","implicit":true,"key":"vgaZRbkzqW"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"大数据微专业的课程体系围绕三条主线展开：","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"VGwpbtJsMH"}],"key":"WXMAO9BuEE"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第一条是数据工程基础。涵盖从数据采集、清洗、存储到调度编排的完整工程链路，让学生理解数据是怎么从原始状态变成可用资产的。","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"key":"E8bOYmdlW2"}],"key":"TU9CzNhtBT"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第二条是数据挖掘与分析。引入我们在真实项目中积累的分析方法和模型实践，强调解决实际业务问题而非纸上谈兵。","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"key":"J7NZzLMiLX"}],"key":"h3uKlMnVVD"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第三条是前沿技术应用。持续把我们在业务中使用大模型处理数据的经验反哺到教学中，保持课程和技术发展同步。","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"VhucwwF3WR"}],"key":"tNjIk6faUQ"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"未来的方向","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"key":"FDVvv1EPCa"}],"identifier":"id","label":"未来的方向","html_id":"id-4","implicit":true,"key":"JvC3ZB7a35"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"课程资料正在和学校合作梳理，未来我们会开源一份量潮版本的课程体系。这不仅是对高校的贡献，也是对我们自己标准化能力的检验——能把隐式的经验提炼成显式的可教学内容，本身就是一种核心竞争力。","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"key":"SWTKs5KMvK"}],"key":"CiuqwZTqPX"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"开源之后，这套体系可以推广到更多有类似需求的高校，形成可复制的产教融合服务模式。","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"key":"QTZ40FRdrB"}],"key":"V679rkozxI"}],"key":"I588b3nWB5"}],"key":"IbQweuqM47"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}